data.description:
Come see this classic rambler, situated on a corner lot and conveniently located in walking distance to tons of nearby shopping. Mature maples frame this home in the front and rear, and a fenced backyard is ideal for kids and pets. Energy efficient vinyl windows have been updated on the main floor, and a new roof (2021), refinished hardwood floors (2018) driveway (2019), and updated sewer line (2018) make this move-in ready. 
Typical of this style, there are 3 bedrooms on the main level (one currently in use as a dining space), and there a lower level bedroom has been added with egress and an ensuite bathroom. The lower level also includes a 21x11 family room and an 8x10 office/flex room. 
Don't miss the 3D tour and floor plan images for room dimensions and layout.
